 out who was in charge of security after 1993 WTC\n\n- 2017 visit to Saudi. touching the orb with King + Egypt.  Visit to Israel followed to to try again (for the 1000th time) for peace middle east\n\n- later in 2017... Vegas shooting/massacre \n\n- later, some saudi royals locked up\nIn hotel prison \n\nQuote a bit more, but this is the framework.  You could bring in qfags here too I suppose...the comments about Awan and saving something for last.\n\nWe are now at this 48 hour presicpice where USA and Iran are essentially threatening to destroy Israel and Iran (infrastructure). \n\nAnd what happens if/when they do?\n\nUN/EU has been warned right? If YOU want to stop it, YOU come help. So when they don't, and when it happens, whose fault is it? \n\nNever Forget. Maybe TRUMP never did. Did you?\n\nNo conspiracy here. Just personal options and observations. I know nothing and do nothing, just like the rest of you (those who arent in armed forces anyway)\n\n\n\n\n", "author": "MRNAH", "created": 1774205794912, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Build_Back_Bankrupt", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": true, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Unpopular Opinion -- TRUMP is going to let Saudi and Egypt be the new property managers of the Middle East.", "last_comment_created": 1774207022901, "content": "<p>Here's some things to consider:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>On 9/11 Trump made statements about what he thought brought the towers down.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>9/11 dancing in celebration of the towers</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Trump called out who was in charge of security after 1993 WTC</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>2017 visit to Saudi. touching the orb with King + Egypt.  Visit to Israel followed to to try again (for the 1000th time) for peace middle east</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>later in 2017... Vegas shooting/massacre</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>later, some saudi royals locked up\nIn hotel prison</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Quote a bit more, but this is the framework.  You could bring in qfags here too I suppose...the comments about Awan and saving something for last.</p>\n<p>We are now at this 48 hour presicpice where USA and Iran are essentially threatening to destroy Israel and Iran (infrastructure).</p>\n<p>And what happens if/when they do?</p>\n<p>UN/EU has been warned right? If YOU want to stop it, YOU come help. So when they don't, and when it happens, whose fault is it?</p>\n<p>Never Forget. Maybe TRUMP never did. Did you?</p>\n<p>No conspiracy here. Just personal options and observations. I know nothing and do nothing, just like the rest of you (those who arent in armed forces anyway)</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 5, "score_up": 15, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2035752977923768327", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASYyyPvYP", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 14, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "", "id": 8506391, "raw_content": "", "author": "LiberaIPussyGuy", "created": 1774207069693, "profile_picture": "kUZP54YGIYuT", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "RandyQuaidsBeard", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASYyyPvYP.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/not_rekt_11/status/2035752977923768327?s=20", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolutio